Increase in smf influence=
	1
	~	
	~		|

Inflow to SMF Influence=
	Increase in smf influence*
	
	Access to Finance*Industry Activities*Renewable fuel in the Energy Mix*
	SMF Compatibility for other vessel types*0.2*
	SMF Compatibility with port infrastructure*0.2*
	SMF Emissions
	/SMF Price Index*
	SMF Regulations*0.2*
	SMF Safety*0.2*
	SMF Technology Readiness Level*0.2* 
	SMF Suitability for Cross Sector applications*0.2*
	10000
	~	
	~	Delay in Inflow to SMF Influence*Access to Finance*Industry Activities*Renewable \
		fuel in the Energy Mix*SMF Compatibility for other vessel types
		*SMF Compatibility with port infrastructure*SMF Regulations*SMF Safety*SMF \
		Suitability for Cross Sector applications*SMF Technology Readiness \
		Level*SMF Emissions/SMF Price Index*SMF Influence
	|

